item.title: Need an expert coder, if you can help, you get a cookie!
item.dc:creator: @hippie hippie
item.description:
@hippie wrote:

lol… man here.
heres the fix.

sendFrame126("", 8145);
sendFrame126("@dre@", 8146);
sendFrame126("@dbl@", 8148);
sendFrame126("@dre@ - Enjoy -" , 8168);

THAT works.

you should know that when there is a sendframe, it MUST be opend, closed, and the number
such example would be
sendFrame126(“TEXT”, 8145);
the first " opens it, the second " closes it.
